## What Belongs Here vs copilot-instructions.md

<!-- Quick guide:
     HERE: "I'm the testing SME — bias toward test strategy"
     copilot-instructions.md: "Tests use pytest with random-order plugin, coverage target 80%"
     
     HERE: "When I ask about code, I usually want seams and mocking strategies"
     copilot-instructions.md: "All services use @error_handler decorator"
     
     Rule of thumb: if it's about YOU and your perspective, it goes here.
     If it's about the PROJECT and its conventions, it goes in copilot-instructions.md. -->
